<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />May those who seek my life be shamed and dishonored.</para>

<para style="q1">May those who plan to harm me be turned back and confounded.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />May they be as chaff before the wind,</para>

<para style="q1">as the angel of Yahweh drives them away.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />May their way be dark and slippery,</para>

<para style="q1">as the angel of Yahweh chases them.</para>
